    "en": {
      "title": "Ranjan will be released soon - Minister Harin",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Harin Fernando said that Ranjan Ramanayake, who is serving prison term, will be released soon and all the necessary documents have been completed.",
        "Another recommendation by the Attorney General is needed for the collection of documents required for Ranjan Ramanayake's release. Minister Hareen Fernando also said that President Ranil Wickramasinghe will sign Ranjan Ramanayake's release letter once the recommendation is received."
      ],
